{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629560/extras/Gif_TowerView.gif?t=1735483941\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play Winter, an invincible god who desperately wants to die, in this cyberpunk RPG Tactics with roguelike elements. Explore the tower city of Shavanath, lead your squad of champions into battle and take control of your godly powers to change the course of Fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629560/extras/Gif_ControlPowers.gif?t=1735483941\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique fighting mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Control a god and his squad of champions; constantly choose between risking the life of your champions against terrible foes, or unleashing your godly powers to one shot almost anyone but potentially destroy the world </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Challenging turn-based combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master a team-based combat system inspired by classic Strategy RPGs where every attack can be fatal to your champions (permadeath within a run, automatic retaliation system)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Roguelite elements</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience unique playthroughs where every attempt to fulfill Winter's wish to die will be different: assemble your own squad of champions, face various cyberpunk foes, and unravel different neigborhoods of the tower city of Shavanath with every run</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629560/extras/Gif_Freyja.gif?t=1735483941\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Excited by this game?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Please consider wishlisting it !</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/im